"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"? 아아, 그렇구나.\n보컬 트레이닝을 하러 가는데 베이스도 짊어져서\n그런 얼굴을 했구나.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"둘 다 연습할 생각이거든.\n노래도, 베이스도.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"기술을 연마하는 것도 중요하지만\n지금은 RAS의 음악에 필요한 걸 갈고 닦고 싶어. ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"베이스에서도 RAS 연주로 맞출 때\n제일 멋지게 올리는 소리를 찾고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"노래도 어떻게 불러야 듣는 사람의 마음에 꽂힐 수 있을까.\n어떻게 하면 곡의 매력을 끌어낼 수 있을까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"그런 걸 생각하면서 연습하고 있어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"어느 쪽이든 어중간하게 하고 싶지 않으니까.\n자기가 납득할 수 있도록 확실히 하는 것뿐이야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"이렇게 매일 진심으로 음악에 임하고 있는 건\nRAS 덕분인 거 같아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"memorial-n-layer-011",